<body>
<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs> column <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs>, with five standing figures within <rs type="decoration">arcade</rs>d embrasures (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">2.19</measure> x <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.92</measure> x <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.98</measure>): a central male <rs type="decoration">figure</rs> flanked by two <rs cert="low" type="decoration">muses</rs> on either side. For full description see bibliography. </p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs>  a. along the upper edge (which is worn and damaged), and b. on either side of the head of the central figure.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Standard forms; <measure precision="circa" dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.01-0.015</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
</div>
<div type="edition" lang="grc">
